`g : ....`, this is a .....

Variant of `hf'.i` when all vertices of the pullback square lie in the image of yoneda. -/
@[reassoc]
lemma w' {X Y Z : C} {f : X ‚ü∂ Z} (g : yoneda.obj Y ‚ü∂ yoneda.obj Z)
    (hf : Presheaf.representable (yoneda.map f)) :
      hf.fst' g ‚â´ f = hf.snd g ‚â´ (Yoneda.fullyFaithful.preimage g) :=
